      "title": "S. Thomas\u2019 down fighting St. Anthony\u2019s to retain Fr. Angelo Rosati trophy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "S. Thomas\u2019 College Mount Lavinia recorded their first win of the ongoing Dialog Schools Rugby tournament with a comfortable 32 points to 25 win over St. Anthony\u2019s in the match played at Havelock Park yesterday. In the process S. Thomas\u2019 retained the Fr. Angelo Rosati trophy."
